metadata.name: All Alone Agaisnt 100 Odds
metadata.description:
I got myself into a fight with zero probability of winning chance. No one stand beside me to cheer on me. How long will I last?, Question that keep replaying on my head. Will the day when light of hope shine upon me ever comes. 

A tiny pebble underneath of a mountain that will never get noticed. Will the day when someone finally pick me up comes true?, I'll never know. Since im standing all alone agaisnt a million of possibilities.
